Package: d6
Title: Template for D6 research projects
Version: 0.1.0.0
Date: 2020-09-16
Authors@R: "Cedric Scherer <cedricphilippscherer@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: This package works as a template for new research
    projects, under the idea of having everything (data, R scripts, functions
    and manuscript/reports) contained in the same package (a 'research compendium')
    to facilitate collaboration and promote reproducibility.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: CC0
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/EcoDynIZW/d6proj
BugReports: https://github.com/EcoDynIZW/d6proj/issues
